{"type": "article", "id": 19331, "title": "壁挂式梳妆柜", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-18T07:30:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 64, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016070213473924T5rghBWRmnuXzC.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这个挂在墙边的方形白色盒子并不引人注意，打开后才会发现里面别有洞天。包括一面镜子、内置灯和小的置物架，可以当做一个小的化妆柜或者是酒柜。拉开柜门就是梳妆的台面，用完后推上去，并不占用空间。很适合旅馆等空间较小的地方，柜子的边长为 40 厘米，<a href=\"http://ambivalenz.org/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145844YV1jyC0w2tM8sOSv.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145844YVcb3N15BxmGAEMv.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145845VkM4EZRC8O6vy7iU.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"731\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.21833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145845eZ8jyt0Q3oBuVbLg.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}